    OTLP_HTTP --> TRACE_PIPELINE
    JAEGER_GRPC --> TRACE_PIPELINE
    JAEGER_HTTP --> TRACE_PIPELINE
    JAEGER_COMPACT --> TRACE_PIPELINE
    ZIPKIN --> TRACE_PIPELINE

    TRACE_PIPELINE --> RESOURCE_DETECT
